OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FStaff shortages could last 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ftwo years, says CBI        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The shortage of workers that is        
OL,6, affecting supply chains across Britain 
OL,7, could last for up to two years,        
OL,8, according to the business body, the    
OL,9, Confederation of British Industry.     
OL,11,FIndustries from pig farming to fast    
OL,12,Ffood have said the lack of skilled     
OL,13,Fstaff is disrupting their business.    
OL,15,FThe CBI said the shortages would harm  
OL,16,Fthe UK's economic recovery.            
OL,18,FIt said the government should adopt a  
OL,19,Fmore flexible policy on immigration to 
OL,20,Ftackle the problem.                    
